data.description: Welcome to this Cozy single-story home that offers a spacious living room, a two-car garage, four bedrooms and two bathrooms! As you walk into the home, a deep entry way will guide you into an open living room with plenty of natural lighting, The kitchen overlooks the dining room  featuring large granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances throughout.  The backyard features a covered patio with plenty of space for large gatherings or for for your pets.
